}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 9116, \"to\": 9128}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 9143, \"to\": 9149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old cemented his place in the showpiece event after crossing the line in third place with a time of 1:43.50m.\", \"from\": 9151, \"to\": 9272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his place\", \"from\": 9176, \"to\": 9185}, {\"ngram\": \"the showpiece event\", \"from\": 9189, \"to\": 9208}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 9224, \"to\": 9232}, {\"ngram\": \"third place\", \"from\": 9236, \"to\": 9247}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 9253, \"to\": 9259}, {\"ngram\": \"1:43.50m.\", \"from\": 9263, \"to\": 9272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not be happier,\\\" Burgin explained before momentarily finding himself lost for words.\", \"from\": 9274, \"to\": 9367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9300, \"end\": 9306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burgin,_Kentucky\", \"score\": 0.8592143791370283, \"rank\": 0.13078149920256973, \"text\": \"Burgin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burgin,_Kentucky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burgin,_Kentucky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 9361, \"to\": 9366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know what to say.\", \"from\": 9368, \"to\": 9395, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's sort of come out of nowhere.\", \"from\": 9396, \"to\": 9429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My fastest time this year has been 1:45m.\", \"from\": 9430, \"to\": 9471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My fastest time\", \"from\": 9430, \"to\": 9445}, {\"ngram\": \"1:45m.\", \"from\": 9465, \"to\": 9471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew I could run faster, but to get through in a PB - and I felt quite good doing it as well - so yeah.\", \"from\": 9472, \"to\": 9577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a PB\", \"from\": 9521, \"to